text: Sydney Kai Kamlager-Dove ( ; born July 20, 1972) is an American politician who became the U.S. representative for California's 37th congressional district since 2023. Sydney Kamlager-Dove was born in Chicago, Illinois. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
